Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.02,0:00:59.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.02,0:00:59.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Incoming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:05.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1036,348)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.50,0:01:07.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  你可真是个大麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton, you're a hot mess
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.22,0:01:13.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷我秘方偷那么多次  全是你活该
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:10.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Serves ya right fer tryin' to steal me formular
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:13.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the gazillionth time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.05,0:01:15.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会复仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:15.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have my revenge
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.37,0:01:17.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.37,0:01:17.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mark my words
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.51,0:01:19.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:19.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.71,0:01:20.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:20.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't over
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.32,0:01:22.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忙活一天累坏了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.32,0:01:22.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hard day at work?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.82,0:01:24.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你需要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.82,0:01:24.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know what you need
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.21,0:01:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦  我偷不到蟹黄堡的秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Karen, I'm never gonna get that Krabby Patty formula
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.77,0:01:46.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,味道不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.77,0:01:46.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not bad
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.29,0:01:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你掉脸皮快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your molten face peels
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.50,0:01:57.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的海滩烧烤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:57.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy clambake
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.37,0:01:59.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:59.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.35,0:02:03.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难道就要被射线恶魔和邪恶帮同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:03.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about to become hero flambé cooked by Man Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.14,0:02:05.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烧成烤肉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:05.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and his criminal posse of E.V.I.L.?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.59,0:02:06.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我烤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:06.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope so
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.18,0:02:10.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱看坏蛋占优势
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:10.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love it when the villains gain the upper hand
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.94,0:02:14.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的英雄面临危机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:14.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As our heroes face certain doom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.30,0:02:18.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同时坏蛋们逃往地下秘密基地去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:18.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the villains escape to their secret underground lair
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.49,0:02:20.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:20.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.74,0:02:24.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只要加入邪恶帮就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:24.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I need to do is join the criminals of E.V.I.L.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.15,0:02:26.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们可以帮我打败老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:26.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They'll help me defeat Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smart thinking
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.02,0:02:29.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以当  毛巾侠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:29.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can go as "Towel Man"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少自作聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be a wisenheimer
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.75,0:02:34.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不披这破布
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:34.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't accessorize this old rag
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.32,0:02:36.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要真衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:36.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a real costume
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.75,0:03:02.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,斗篷还是得改短点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:02.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe a shorter cape
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.45,0:03:08.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里一定就是他们秘密基地入口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:08.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This must be the entrance to their secret lair
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.90,0:03:11.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,潜进垃圾箱里就能进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:11.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little dumpster dive, and I'm in
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.97,0:03:18.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,门在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:18.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(686,374)}邪恶帮基地\N在这
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.16,0:03:25.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找错垃圾箱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:25.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wrong dumpster
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.60,0:03:28.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:28.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1112,372)}秘密基地
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.37,0:03:31.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:31.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:32.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1042,340)}邪恶帮                   继续走                      往这边
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.17,0:03:35.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是来加入邪恶帮的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:35.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm here to join the forces of E.V.I.L.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:38.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(416,594)}舞台大门
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.14,0:03:40.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:40.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dude
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.85,0:03:41.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:41.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.60,0:03:43.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,登记完好好等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:43.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sign in and wait your turn
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,红皮革  黄皮革
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Red leather, yellow leather
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.28,0:03:47.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人给我下车
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:47.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of the car, fellas
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.23,0:03:49.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把钱都交出来  放进袋子里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:49.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take all your money and put it in the bag
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错  海绵宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Mr. Bob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.36,0:03:52.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要炸了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:52.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I expect you to fry
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.07,0:03:53.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等到满月升起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:53.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When the full moon rises
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am the Strangler
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.12,0:03:57.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:57.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the Strangler
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.54,0:04:01.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这黄色的是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:01.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this yellow thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.62,0:04:03.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,某种霉菌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:03.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some kind of mold?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生存还是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To be or--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.84,0:04:05.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,提词
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:05.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,line
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.30,0:04:15.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来的这一大票流氓挺出色  对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:11.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:15.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,quite an impressive rogues gallery up there, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.30,0:04:19.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢你们从见不得人的日程中抽空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:19.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,out of your scandalous schedules
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来邪恶帮面试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to try out for E.V.I.L.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.28,0:04:22.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,众所周知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:22.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As you all know
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶帮新人选只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we can only pick one new villain to join Team E.V.I.L.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.12,0:04:29.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就开始面试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:29.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so let the judging begin
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点到谁就选谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eeny, meeny, miney--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺斯费拉图
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nosferatu
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.49,0:04:39.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  射线恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:39.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No way, Man Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.95,0:04:41.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才最先
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:41.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was first
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最先走人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First to go bye-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be gone
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺斯费拉图  继续
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nosferatu, proceed
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.65,0:05:04.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哑剧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:04.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mime?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他邪恶超能力就是演哑剧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mime is his evil power?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,螳螂机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Robot Mantis
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.67,0:05:33.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:33.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How dare you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.67,0:05:37.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钢琴好不容易才调好音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:37.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We just had that piano tuned
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点到谁就选谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eeny, meeny, miney--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢尔顿痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sheldon J. Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.87,0:05:52.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:52.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.75,0:05:53.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:53.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,配乐就用不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,music won't be necessary
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.79,0:05:57.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:57.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.72,0:06:00.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问你的坏蛋超能力是什么  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:06:00.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So what's your supervillain power, little guy?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.27,0:06:06.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我敢说这超能力是我的邪恶大智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:03.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd venture to say
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:06.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it would be my massive, evil intellect
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.67,0:06:09.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出彩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:09.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Impressive
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.07,0:06:12.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你对你未来五年的方向有何愿景
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:12.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So where do you see yourself in the next five years?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.47,0:06:16.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一旦我最终得到了秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:16.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, once I finally have the secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.35,0:06:21.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最终导致的末世后的全球毁灭帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:19.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The post-apocalyptic global empire
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:21.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of destruction that results
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就将会是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will be mine
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.35,0:06:27.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而我将风风光光坐在你们的尸骨堆上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll be sitting pretty on a pile of your bones
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一听就有反派本色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds pretty villainous
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.02,0:06:34.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  你可以进入测试阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:34.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, you'll move on to the test phase
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.08,0:06:37.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但首先得先取个像样的坏蛋名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:37.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But first, you'll need a proper supervillain name
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.60,0:06:40.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要  绿豆先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:40.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about "Mr. Green Bean"?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.89,0:06:44.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小咪咪的绿绿人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.89,0:06:44.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The "Itsy Bitsy Green Guy"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, too long
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.25,0:06:48.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不然就  小个子队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:48.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about "Captain Pipsqueak"?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.17,0:06:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.55,0:06:49.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:49.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That settles it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.40,0:06:53.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小个子队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:53.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Captain Pipsqueak
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小个子队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Captain Pipsqueak
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.43,0:06:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,之后应该会再调整吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can tweak that later, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.37,0:07:00.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  全体成员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:00.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, team
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.70,0:07:04.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,测试小个子队长真实世界中的恶行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:03.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's test Captain Pipsqueak's villainy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:07.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(844,212)}婴儿宝宝乐园
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.62,0:07:10.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一项测试是给我们买午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:10.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your first test is to get us lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.32,0:07:15.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去儿童乐园买个25磅的全家桶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:15.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a 25-pound bucket from Weenie Hut Jr.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加邪恶酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With Evil sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.52,0:07:19.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多加邪恶酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:19.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Extra Evil sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.80,0:07:23.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这恶行挺怪  不过没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:23.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Odd caper, but no problemo
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来份25磅儿童热狗全家桶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a 25-pound Weenie bucket, please
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做好点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and make it snappy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.52,0:07:34.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多加邪恶酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:34.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And extra Evil sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这单我认得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know that order
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.47,0:07:39.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是邪恶帮成员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:39.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're one of those E.V.I.L. guys
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们一律禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're all banned
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(750,686)}绝不为邪恶帮提供食品
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.72,0:07:43.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快把餐给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:43.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just give me my order
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.70,0:07:46.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然就有你好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:46.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or you'll know the meaning of fear
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.87,0:07:49.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.87,0:07:49.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Security
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.12,0:07:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个小小的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got a small problem here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.12,0:08:00.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:00.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So boring
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.02,0:08:00.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,腿太短
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:00.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Short legs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.66,0:08:01.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早该知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:01.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We should've known better
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.74,0:08:02.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都快饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:02.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm starving here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.23,0:08:05.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他买到吃的的可能性有多大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:05.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are the chances he gets our food?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.22,0:08:07.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大概几乎没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:07.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Slim to none, I'm guessing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.25,0:08:08.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:08.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁来帮我拿下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could somebody help me with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\pos(608,750)}25{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}磅儿童热狗\N全家桶
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.30,0:08:19.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多加邪恶酱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:19.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And extra Evil sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.68,0:08:20.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太邪恶了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:20.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wicked
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.30,0:08:20.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:20.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Awesome
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.86,0:08:24.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为小个子队长干热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:24.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Weenie toast to Captain Pipsqueak
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.19,0:08:26.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:26.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pip pip hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  队长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Cap
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿了这袋蜗牛粑粑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,take this bag of snail droppings
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.85,0:08:35.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放到那边那个台阶上面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:35.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and leave it on that doorstep over there
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.22,0:08:37.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里是脚侠家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:37.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the house of the Foot
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是做好事的超级英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's a superhero do-gooder
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,理应让我们狠狠搞他一手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who deserves our worst
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.75,0:08:57.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:57.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.65,0:09:02.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我往袋子里加了点特制海霸糊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:02.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I added a little of my own special Chum Mix to the bag
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.60,0:09:06.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小个子队长  欢迎加入邪恶帮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:06.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Captain Pipsqueak, welcome to E.V.I.L.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.05,0:09:07.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全称是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:07.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which stands for
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.75,0:09:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶人皆为大废物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Every Villain Is Lemons"
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.62,0:09:11.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:11.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.67,0:09:14.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么小个子队长  接下来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:14.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So Captain Pipsqueak, what's next?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.45,0:09:19.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我一起统治世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:19.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Follow me to world domination
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:22.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(572,390)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.16,0:09:29.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又怎么了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:29.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What now, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.87,0:09:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可震惊到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shiver me's lumbers
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.65,0:09:51.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快把秘密配方交出来  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:51.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You might as well give us the secret formula now, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.37,0:09:54.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是邪恶帮的新主谋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:54.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the new mastermind of E.V.I.L.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么  你们几个阿宅要去漫展了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What, you nerds going to a comic convention?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,衣服不错  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is a nice costume, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.58,0:10:05.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫我小个子队长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:05.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The name is Captain Pipsqueak to you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.92,0:10:06.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:06.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肮脏泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dirty Bubble?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.42,0:10:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才刚洗好衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I just did my laundry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.67,0:10:14.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:14.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thieves
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.75,0:10:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的肮脏烂手别来碰我秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep yer filthy, rotten mitts offa me formular
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.11,0:10:24.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:24.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.25,0:10:26.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:26.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.20,0:10:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是统治世界的秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't the formula for world domination
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.65,0:10:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是三明治的秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a recipe for a sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.25,0:10:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How does that work?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.52,0:10:40.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  有了秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:40.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, with that
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.95,0:10:42.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就能让这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:42.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can put this guy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.66,0:10:43.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停业
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:43.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Outta business
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.64,0:10:46.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:46.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why would we ever wanna do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.44,0:10:48.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡可好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:48.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These Krabby Patties taste great
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.63,0:10:49.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:49.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.40,0:10:57.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还给你  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:57.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, boss
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.82,0:10:58.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:58.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.92,0:10:59.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续多做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:10:59.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.27,0:11:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不敢相信这个唬烂小个子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this lousy pipsqueak
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,浪费我们时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wasted our time
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可真是个犯罪天才
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some criminal genius he is
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.00,0:11:07.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.67,0:11:11.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还邪恶大智慧呢  净瞎说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:11.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Massive evil intellect," my eye
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.17,0:11:14.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的哈瓦那辣酱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:14.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy habanero
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.05,0:11:17.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板注定要被困在瓶中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:17.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is Plankton forever doomed to be bound by a bottle?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.62,0:11:19.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要被关进玻璃里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:19.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grounded in glass?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.67,0:11:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.00,0:11:23.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要被裹进邪恶酱里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:23.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enveloped by extra Evil sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.07,0:11:28.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准外带调料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:28.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No outside condiments
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.87,0:11:34.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒霉透了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:34.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this stinks
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:38.59,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FF97&}海底飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(725.802,362)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(739.802,656)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:44.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(759.802,668)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(631.802,468)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:42.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(743.802,534)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(981.802,656)}联合监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(275.802,510)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(659.802,540)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.87,0:11:51.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  多美好的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:51.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, what a beautiful morning
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.55,0:11:53.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:53.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to check the mail
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.17,0:11:55.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道谁在暗恋你了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:55.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and see who loves you, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.72,0:12:00.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道能不能退给寄件人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:12:00.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can return to sender
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.97,0:12:12.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要回去睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:12.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going back to bed now
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睡一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forever
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.27,0:12:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不开邮件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna open your mail?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.72,0:12:21.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:21.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gimme that
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们早都开完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks like you already did
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.40,0:12:27.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我赢奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:27.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:30.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(800,186)}你获胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:30.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(658,886)}机票\N座号{\fnArial}2B
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.57,0:12:30.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我没参加比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:30.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I didn't enter any contest
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.35,0:12:32.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以去免费旅游
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:32.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's an all-expenses-paid trip
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.82,0:12:36.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看美丽的波拉波拉海滩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:36.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to see beautiful Bora Bora Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.12,0:12:39.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们替你参加的  而且只参加了六千次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:39.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We entered it for you, and only 6,000 times too
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, a winner
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.97,0:12:47.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去热带度假胜地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:47.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at a tropical resort
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.07,0:12:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.92,0:12:52.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,获胜家庭将前往裤头村机场与
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.92,0:12:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"The winning family will board 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:52.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at Bikini Bottom Airport and the"--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.55,0:12:56.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,获胜家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:56.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Winning family"?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.50,0:13:00.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是不是忘了说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:13:00.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did we forget to mention
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.73,0:13:03.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:03.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.57,0:13:05.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:05.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I cannot believe
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.89,0:13:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我让你们俩臭鱼烂虾骗进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I let you bottom-feeders talk me into this
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.35,0:13:12.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了你这样的朋友最起码也要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:12.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the least we could do for a friend like you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.55,0:13:15.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  为了你这样的爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:15.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, for a dad like you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.47,0:13:17.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:17.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.68,0:13:18.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:18.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you morons--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.44,0:13:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友  打住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,children, please
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.57,0:13:21.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:21.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:24.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(810,750)}机票
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.12,0:13:27.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位旅客请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:27.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, passengers
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.15,0:13:32.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来见见海底航空大赛获胜者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:32.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Meet Underwater Air's big contest winner
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.55,0:13:37.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥和他的可爱一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:37.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward Tentacles and his adorable family
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位宝爸快来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Dad
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.39,0:13:43.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你跟你家孩子拍张照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:43.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get a picture of you and the kids
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加到机上杂志里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for our in-flight magazine
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.59,0:13:50.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:50.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.92,0:13:53.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说  我爱我家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:53.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,say, "I love my family"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.31,0:13:55.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:55.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.52,0:13:57.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:57.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱我家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love my family
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.42,0:14:12.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你坐我位子上了  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:12.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you're in my seat, Pop
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.65,0:14:17.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我坐过道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:17.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'll take the aisle
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.30,0:14:20.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸坐在中间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:20.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy's in the middle
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.57,0:14:21.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:21.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.67,0:14:23.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这趟航班我绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:23.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am not suffering a whole flight
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.95,0:14:26.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,夹在你们俩个呆头中间受苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:26.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,between you two barnacle brains
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.09,0:14:28.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码让我坐过道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:28.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least give me the aisle
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.64,0:14:33.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是否坐在指定的位置上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:33.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you in your assigned seat?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.05,0:14:43.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  各位旅客
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:43.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.25,0:14:45.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请系好安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:45.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,please fasten your seat belts
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.10,0:14:48.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以调节这个容易拉的带子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:48.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by adjusting this easy-to-pull strap
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.07,0:14:51.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要往紧了系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:51.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make sure it's nice and tight
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.63,0:14:55.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保持座位直立
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:55.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And keep your seat in the upright position
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.32,0:14:57.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,否则后果自负
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:57.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or else
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.75,0:14:58.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:58.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.87,0:15:03.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:03.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These look good
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  要不要换个位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, wanna switch
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.39,0:15:15.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我看窗外风景
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:15.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can look out the window?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.52,0:15:16.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:16.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.79,0:15:17.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过要快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:17.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But hurry
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.77,0:15:27.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位旅客请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:27.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention all passengers
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.37,0:15:28.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:28.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.22,0:15:29.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本次航班的机长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:29.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your captain speaking
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请保持你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please keep your, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.72,0:15:31.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安全带系牢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:31.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,seat belts fastened
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,即将
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as we, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.86,0:15:34.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,升空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:34.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,gain altitude
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.47,0:15:44.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,旅途愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:44.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your flight
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可以逛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You may now roam about the, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.77,0:15:47.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,座舱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:47.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cabin
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.13,0:15:48.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见没  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:48.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hear that, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.34,0:15:50.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以解开安全带了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:50.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can take your seat belt off now
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.45,0:15:50.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:50.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.85,0:15:51.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我解开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:51.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Untie me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.77,0:15:57.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  饲料袋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:57.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, a feed bag
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.52,0:16:07.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}不眠不休的十二小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能小点声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep it down, will ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.90,0:16:16.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:16.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm tryin' to sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.27,0:16:23.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我梦见我在海里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:23.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was in the ocean
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.15,0:16:24.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:24.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now I gotta pee
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.22,0:16:32.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:32.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I help you with something?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要上厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I gotta use a bathroom
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.90,0:16:37.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:37.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rude
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was here first
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.69,0:16:48.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位旅客  另一位空姐怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:48.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy, what happened to the other flight attendant?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她在上卫生间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's in the bathroom
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.11,0:17:06.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空姐会救我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:06.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The flight attendants will save me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.33,0:17:11.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,按呼叫按钮就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:11.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just need to hit that call button
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.32,0:17:16.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上好  先生先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:16.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Mr. Sir
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.15,0:17:19.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要现磨咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:19.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fresh coffee?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.69,0:17:20.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:20.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.20,0:17:23.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  真的空姐哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:23.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, where are the real flight attendants?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.23,0:17:25.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她们上卫生间上了好一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:25.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They've been in the bathroom for a while
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.90,0:17:29.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是咖啡喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:29.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think they had too much coffee
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.89,0:17:32.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这瓶咖啡你要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.89,0:17:32.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now how about that coffee?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I don't want--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.07,0:17:37.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哇  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:37.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wow, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.52,0:17:39.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也太爱咖啡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:39.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you really like coffee
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.65,0:17:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位旅客
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Folks
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.10,0:17:44.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉遇上了强烈水流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:44.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that turbulence
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.75,0:17:47.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:47.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.52,0:17:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你当上空姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They made you a flight attendant?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.76,0:17:53.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也想当吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:53.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You wanna be one too?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.87,0:17:55.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:55.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our apologies, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.44,0:18:11.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮你弄干
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:11.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get you dried off
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.92,0:18:22.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:22.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm free
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm free
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点心时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snack time
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.20,0:18:39.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:39.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.07,0:18:43.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要找机长投诉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:43.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am filing a complaint with the captain
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.72,0:18:45.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我推去驾驶舱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:45.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Roll me to the front of the plane
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:56.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1376,328)}飞行员
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.60,0:19:00.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们旅途是否愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:19:00.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you enjoying your flight?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.11,0:19:01.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:01.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I am not
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.85,0:19:04.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自打起飞  这俩就一直在闹事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:03.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These two have been nothing but trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:04.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,since we took off
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.83,0:19:08.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在他们又在顶替空姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:08.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now they've replaced the flight attendants
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.77,0:19:11.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们对空姐怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:11.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did they do with them?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.62,0:19:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只开了卫生间门  机长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just opened the bathroom door, Captain
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.32,0:19:16.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:16.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like this
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.65,0:19:35.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人开飞机了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:35.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no one flying the plane
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.65,0:19:41.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:41.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.73,0:19:43.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快坠毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:43.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna crash
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.27,0:19:47.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该可以想办法开飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:47.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I can figure this out
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.24,0:19:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  这又有什么难的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, how hard could it be?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.95,0:19:59.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  相信你的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:59.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, trust your instincts
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.07,0:20:02.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:02.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I suppose, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥你看  就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Squidward, we're almost there
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要让飞机着陆就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now all you gotta do is land this thing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别把大家给害死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And not kill everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.40,0:20:23.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:23.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.45,0:20:32.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:32.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, Squidward
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:46.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1256,350)}波拉波拉海滩
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.40,0:20:51.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,耶  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:51.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yay, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波拉波拉海滩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bora Bora Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.80,0:21:01.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位旅客请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:01.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, passengers
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.95,0:21:04.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是你们的新任机长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:04.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is your new captain speaking
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.61,0:21:08.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现已抵达美丽的波拉波拉海滩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:08.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have arrived at beautiful Bora Bora Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.37,0:21:14.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:14.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.39,0:21:16.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞机明明停好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:16.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I stopped this thing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.03,0:21:18.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.03,0:21:18.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, look
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.90,0:21:22.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来一直飞机都是自动驾驶模式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:22.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was on auto-pilot the whole time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:22.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958,520)}自动驾驶     开
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.65,0:21:24.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,耶  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:24.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yay, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.24,0:21:26.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么都没干
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:26.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.25,0:21:29.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:29.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.99,0:21:33.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要下飞机  畅玩度假胜地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:33.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need to get off this plane and enjoy the resort
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.92,0:21:35.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这又何必呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:35.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now why would you wanna do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.50,0:21:39.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这趟旅游只能去看波拉波拉海滩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:39.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You won a trip to see Bora Bora Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.45,0:21:41.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住是住不了的  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:41.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not stay there, silly
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.51,0:21:44.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:44.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And there it goes
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.79,0:21:47.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,造化就爱弄人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:47.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Life is funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.66,0:22:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是本次航班的空姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is your flight attendant speaking
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.56,0:22:05.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,目前正在遭遇逆风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.56,0:22:05.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're experiencing some headwinds
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.05,0:22:12.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,预计前往裤头村的返程需要24小时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the present estimate
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:12.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for our return flight to Bikini Bottom is 24 hours
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.71,0:22:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
